@startuml seq_02_local_sign_in
title Sequence Diagram: UC-02.1 Sign In (Local)

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Auth Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth Service" as Service
participant "User Repository" as Repo
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis

User -> Frontend: Enter username/email and password
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/auth/login {identifier, password}
Controller -> Service: Login User
Service -> Repo: Find User by email or username
Repo --> Service: User found (hashed_password)
Service -> Service: Verify password (bcrypt)
Service -> Service: Generate Access & Refresh Tokens
Service -> Redis: Store Auth State (Refresh Token)
Service --> Controller: Tokens & User Info
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> User: Redirect to Home Page
@enduml